posts.description:
On March 8-10, the Cloud Next event will take place in San Francisco. It is an event that brings together developers, executives, customers, partners, IT decision makers, and Google engineers to build the future of the cloud. Attendees will see what's coming from the Google Cloud Platform, G Suite, Maps, and Devices teams.

Agenda : 
=======
6:00 PM Registration and ice breaking
7:00 PM Start of the keynote live steaming 
8:30 PM tech talk about the cloud 
9:00 PM closing

Amazon S3 is down, and impacting many sites as a result.
Ironically, http://isitdownrightnow.com/ is actually down because of the outage.
Affected services include Slack, Quora,Trello, Twitch, Medium, Amazon Video, Mashable and many more.
